Package org.bukkit

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BlockChangeDelegate
    A delegate for handling block changes.
    Chunk
    Represents a chunk of blocks
    ChunkSnapshot
    Represents a static, thread-safe snapshot of chunk of blocks Purpose is to allow clean, efficient copy of a chunk data to be made, and then handed off for processing in another thread (e.g. map rendering)
    OfflinePlayer  
    Server
    Represents a server implementation
    TravelAgent  
    World
    Represents a world, which may contain entities, chunks and blocks
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bukkit
    Represents the Bukkit core, for version and Server singleton handling
    Location
    Represents a 3-dimensional position in a world
    Note
    A note class to store a specific note.
    WorldCreator
    Represents various types of options that may be used to create a world.
